==== hyperbricks config {!{hypermedia}} ====
hypermedia = <HYPERMEDIA>
hypermedia.head {
    10 = <CSS>
    10.inline = <<[
        body {
            background-color: lightblue;
        }
    ]>>
}
==== explainer ====
Use inline to define css in a multiline block <<[ /* css goes here */ ]>>
